nodes.text: The Fobosi District was a district on the planet Coruscant adjacent to The Works.

The Fobosi District contained the elite centers of business and commerce planning for Coruscant and the Galactic Republic as a whole. It was the location of the Skydome Botanical Gardens, the headquarters of the Order of the Canted Circle, the Fobosi District Medcenter, and the central administration building of the University of Coruscant.
